                    <header><div><h2>JONES</h2></div></header>
                    <div class="jones">
                        
                        <img class="rev" width="760" height="760" src="https://i0.wp.com/strayanimalfoundationindia.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/jones.jpg?w=960&ssl=1"> 
                        <div>
                            <div class="jones-content">
                                <p >Our sweet Jones visited vet for followup. He said Jones leg is recovering well. While we cannot bring his spine back, we are making sure he is pain-free and comfortable. Great news is we found a sanctuary for Jones. Once he recovers, he will go to sanctuary to live for life. Jones is fortunate to get a sanctuary. Any donations will help Jones sanctuary fees. Please donate and help Jones go to sanctuary.
                                    When a Good Samaritan came across Jones’s lifeless body lying in the streets, without hesitation, he ran to his rescue. But, sadly, this sweet boy needed way more than simple first aid…
                                    Without seconds to spare, rescuers at Stray Animal Foundation of India were called to help get this sweet boy the extensive medical care he desperately needed. After rushing Jones to the vet for an evaluation, x-rays revealed he’s suffering from a spine vertebra dislocation and a hind leg fracture. Jones immediately received a splint to not only immobilize the fracture to protect it from any further injury but also allowing it to heal by keeping the broken ends together and in alignment. </p>
                            </div>
                        
                    </div>
